{
  "stem": "17543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One done this, another one that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So on the top, it was completely covered up in big bales of cotton wools, covered up, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] covered up the-- in a-- and a canvas covers up these big bales of wool.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somebody else had to put on a wheelbarrow and take it to the storage place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was only, I only know what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was that machine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all night-- I was only 13-- all night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with that little soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how I had the energy, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went in the evenings and came back in the mornings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what time we went, what time we left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only good thing was, in this place was hot and cold water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could, we drink as much as we like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was hot water and we could wash our hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because time till time, these German soldiers went off to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we was left with the workers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they not taken any notice of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So if we switched off the machine and then just go in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because by then, a little bit my hair was growing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with some liquid soap-- so I just put on my head and washed it, like the others, in turn, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So at least we had warm water, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was better, was better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is, this was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, it wasn't good, but it was a bit better.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Warm water, and we had that clothes, that striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least we was covered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And had that wooden boots sort on, so our feet was warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A work camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
